instructions: Place the charger on the table.
Place the dinner fork to the left of the charger.
Place the dinner knife to the right of the charger.
Place the salad fork to the left of the dinner fork.
Place the salad knife to the right of the dinner knife.
Place the soup spoon to the right of the salad knife.
Place the desert spoon on the table, above the charger.
Plave the desert fork on the table below the desert spoon, but above the charger.
Place the bread plate on the table above the forks, and to the left of the desert utensils.
Place the butter knife on the bread plate.
Place the water glass on the table above the knifes, and to the right of the desert utensils.
Place the napkin on the plate.
